Package org.apache.juneau.bean.html5

package org.apache.juneau.bean.html5
HTML5 Data Transfer Objects

This package contains predefined DTOs for working with HTML5 elements and structures. These classes provide a convenient way to serialize and parse HTML5 content using Juneau's marshalling framework.
